1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,200
Bacteria evolve fast – faster than our antibiotics.

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:05,200
This isn't just science fiction.

3
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:07,600
It's happening now with antibiotic resistance.

4
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:13,600
Every time we misuse antibiotics, we create selection pressure, speeding up the evolution of superbugs.

5
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:18,400
The CDC warns that these superbugs could lead to untreatable infections worldwide.

6
00:00:18,400 --> 00:00:19,600
But there's hope.

7
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:22,000
Good stewardship can slow this process.

8
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:23,200
Use antibiotics wisely.

9
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:27,200
Stay informed, share this knowledge, and help fight antibiotic resistance.
